OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FThousands of households can now safely
OL,8,Fuse and drink their tap water without
OL,9,Fhaving to boil it first after a .
OL,11,F(SWW) said around 14,500 households in
OL,12,Fthe Alston supply area can now use
OL,13,Ftheir tap water safely, although some
OL,14,F2,500 properties in Hillhead, upper
OL,15,Fparts of and Kingswear should continue
OL,16,Fto boil their supply before drinking
