OL,3,CBoil-water notice lifted after water
OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FDevon MP Anthony Mangnall said the
OL,8,Fregional water supplier's response to
OL,9,Fthe outbreak has been "contemptible
OL,10,Fand just generally incompetent" as he
OL,11,Fcalled for them to be "on the line" to
OL,12,Fhelp compensate local businesses.
OL,14,FAbout 16,000 households and businesses
OL,15,Fin the Brixham area of Devon, supplied
OL,16,Fby SWW had been told not to use their
OL,17,Ftap water for drinking without boiling
OL,18,Fand cooling it first.
