OL,7,FA decision was made in consultation
OL,8,Fwith the UK Health Security Agency
OL,9,F(UKHSA) and the local authority's
OL,10,Fenvironmental health department to
OL,11,Flift the boil-water warning for most
OL,12,Fhouseholds on Saturday (May 18).
