OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FSWW chief customer officer Laura
OL,8,FFlowerdew said: "Following rigorous
OL,9,Ftesting this week, it is now safe to
OL,10,Flift the boil water notice in the
OL,11,FAlston water supply area. This
OL,12,Fdecision has been supported by the
OL,13,FGovernment's public health experts and
OL,14,Fthe local authority's environmental
OL,15,Fhealth department.
OL,17,F"This situation has caused an immense
OL,18,Famount of disruption, distress and
OL,19,Fanxiety. We are truly sorry this has
OL,20,Fhappened.
