OL,3,CBoil-water notice lifted after water
OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"The public rightly expect a safe,
OL,8,Fclean and reliable source of drinking
OL,9,Fwater and on this occasion, we have
OL,10,Ffallen significantly short of
OL,11,Fexpectations. We will not stop working
OL,12,Funtil this has been fully resolved.
OL,14,F"With the boil water notice still in
OL,15,Fplace in Hillhead, upper parts of
OL,16,FBrixham and Kingswear, we are urging
OL,17,Fcustomers who are unsure if they are
OL,18,Fstill affected to visit the postcode
OL,19,Fchecker on our website or call us so
OL,20,Fwe can check for them."
