OL,3,CBoil-water notice lifted after water
OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fsaid on Friday that 46 cases of
OL,9,Fcryptosporidium, a disease which can
OL,10,Fcause unpleasant symptoms such as
OL,11,Fdiarrhoea and vomiting, had been
OL,12,Fconfirmed in the town and that more
OL,13,Fcases were anticipated.
OL,15,F'Failed to safeguard public health'
OL,17,FConservative MP Anthony Mangnall,
OL,18,Fwhose Totnes constituency includes
OL,19,FBrixham, said SWW's response to the
OL,20,Fparasite outbreak in the seaside town
OL,21,Fhad been inadequate.
