OL,3,CBoil-water notice lifted after water
OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FHe said on Saturday: "The predominant
OL,8,Ffailure is the fact that earlier in
OL,9,Fthe week, South West Water was asked
OL,10,Fwhether or not this was to do with
OL,11,Ftheir network and they categorically
OL,12,Fruled it out, only for them to change
OL,13,Ftheir position 24 hours later, which I
OL,14,Fthink is contemptible and just
OL,15,Fgenerally incompetent ` and it's put a
OL,16,Flot of people's health at risk."
