OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FMr Mangnall said SWW had failed to
OL,8,F"safeguard public health" and would
OL,9,F"be absolutely on the line" to
OL,10,Fcompensate local businesses which have
OL,11,Flost money because of the outbreak.
OL,13,FThe MP said he would be raising the
OL,14,Fmatter in the House of Commons and
OL,15,Fwith the area's local authorities but
OL,16,Fwas "absolutely determined not to jump
OL,17,Fthe gun on this".
