OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FIt said on Saturday a water tank at
OL,8,FHillhead reservoir ` where infected
OL,9,Fwater had been detected ` had been
OL,10,Fdrained overnight.
OL,12,FDavid Harris, drought and resilience
OL,13,Fdirector at the water company, said:
OL,14,F"Over the past four days, we have been
OL,15,Fworking tirelessly to identify and
OL,16,Fresolve this issue. We are deeply
OL,17,Fsorry for the impact this disruption
OL,18,Fis having on daily lives.
