OL,3,CBoil-water notice lifted after water
OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"As part of our ongoing investigation,
OL,8,Fa damaged valve on private land has
OL,9,Fbeen identified as the possible cause,
OL,10,Fwhich has since been isolated from the
OL,11,Fnetwork and repaired.
OL,13,F"As you would expect, we are urgently
OL,14,Finvestigating how this happened, while
OL,15,Fworking to rule out any other possible
OL,16,Fsources of contamination elsewhere in
OL,17,Fthe network."
