OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FDr Lincoln Sargeant, Torbay's director
OL,8,Fof public health, told BBC Radio 4's
OL,9,FToday Programme the initial
OL,10,Fcontamination has been "more or less
OL,11,Fdealt with" but delays in symptoms
OL,12,Fdeveloping may cause the number of
OL,13,Fcases to increase for "up to two
OL,14,Fweeks".
OL,16,FShadow environment secretary Steve
OL,17,FReed called on the Government to "put
OL,18,Fwater companies under special
OL,19,Fmeasures" following the outbreak.
