OL,4,Ccompany's 'contemptible' outbreak
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FHe said: "Despite warnings, the
OL,8,FConservatives just folded their arms
OL,9,Fand looked the other way while water
OL,10,Fcompanies pumped a tidal wave of raw
OL,11,Fsewage into our rivers, lakes and seas
OL,12,F` putting lives at risk.
OL,14,F"The Government must urgently adopt
OL,15,FLabour's plan to put the water
OL,16,Fcompanies under special measures to
OL,17,Fclean up water.
