OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"The next Labour government will
OL,8,Fstrengthen regulation so law-breaking
OL,9,Fwater bosses face criminal charges,
OL,10,Fand give the regulator new powers to
OL,11,Fblock the payment of any bonuses until
OL,12,Fwater bosses have cleaned up their
OL,13,Ffilth.
OL,15,F"With Labour, the polluter ` not the
OL,16,Fpublic ` will pay."
