OL,7,FSally Dart, who runs homewares shop
OL,8,FFlotsam 50 near Brixham Harbour, said
OL,9,Fbusiness was "probably 30 to 40% down"
OL,10,Fand described the water company as
OL,11,F"appalling".
OL,13,FMs Dart said locals first felt
OL,14,Fsymptoms after a busy, pirate festival
OL,15,Fheld in the town between May 4 and 6.
OL,17,FReferring to SWW, she added: "They
OL,18,Fknew they had this problem ` obviously
OL,19,Fthe reservoir couldn't cope for some
OL,20,Freason or another, it was getting all
OL,21,Fthe stuff off the field into it.
